title: Enable Margin Bell (MARGIN_BELL)
---
body:

Enables an indicator when the cursor moves near the right margin.

When enabled the terminal will sounds its bell (or do a similar notification) when the cursor crosses from not near the right margin to near the right margin.

See {{seq_link('csi_su_t_space')}} for additional settings.
